Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.41,0:06:02.77,little,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,600)\pos(482,192)}妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.86,0:00:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也是好天气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.10,0:00:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥  老哥  不快点起来的话要迟到了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.83,0:00:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候你即使被高桥老师骂了我可不管喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.87,0:00:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.65,0:00:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这周大概全国地区都会是晴天  
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.11,0:00:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过从周末到下周初  局部地区可能有时有雨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.93,0:00:52.33,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}因为工作关系 \N 先出门咯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.54,0:01:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥  你还没起来吗 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.72,0:01:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美也 先出发咯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.72,0:01:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊  已经这么晚啦… 为啥不叫醒我…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.61,0:01:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有准时叫你的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.10,0:01:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人  我可没这印象
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.30,0:01:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有准时叫你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.54,0:01:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.57,0:01:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.61,0:01:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.83,0:01:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不快点走的话要迟到咯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.52,0:01:39.03,uta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\an2}君は君のままで  僕は僕のままで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.09,0:01:45.39,uta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\an2}全てわかり合えたら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.60,0:01:53.73,uta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\an2}何度も季節を重ねたね  あの日から
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.76,0:01:59.96,uta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\an2}今日までどうもありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.74,0:02:07.86,uta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\an2}狭い路地裏目指し  白い息が踊る
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.88,0:02:13.32,uta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\an2}痛いくらい握った手をひいて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.33,0:02:15.32,uta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\an2}君は進んでいく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.40,0:02:18.37,uta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\an2}今すぐkissしたかった
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.44,0:02:22.27,uta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\an2}隠れた自販機の裏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.33,0:02:25.61,uta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\an2}ハニかんで見つめあった
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.62,0:02:31.06,uta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\an2}優しいキモチ溢れた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.19,0:02:38.19,uta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\an2}君は君のままで  僕は僕のままで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.22,0:02:43.51,uta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\an2}全て分かり合えたなら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.52,0:02:45.48,uta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\an2}2人は1つだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.50,0:02:48.92,uta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\an2}どんな小さな幸せも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.96,0:02:52.42,uta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\an2}見つけ出せる気がするよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.45,0:02:57.88,uta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\an2}優しくなれたのは  君のおかげ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.50,0:03:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.04,0:03:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧  老哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.17,0:03:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一早就从楼梯上摔下来  真倒霉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.94,0:03:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有准时叫你的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.94,0:03:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你没准时叫我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.36,0:03:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了有叫你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.68,0:03:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟  你们俩还是一如既往地一早就相亲相爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.84,0:03:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.93,0:03:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你来这招？  真来这招？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.60,0:03:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么这个你也会当作不认识吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.82,0:03:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.21,0:03:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是苦苦哀求我老哥  好不容易才弄到手的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.56,0:03:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  心灵挚友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.23,0:03:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥们真浅显易懂啊  
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.62,0:03:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是宝贝书的话题？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.83,0:03:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美也  这对男人来说可是永远的主题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.92,0:03:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不如说是不得不追求的「哔」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.42,0:03:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对  从神话时代开始
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.31,0:03:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直延续到现在的宇宙的真理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.16,0:03:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.85,0:03:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  老哥这样没问题吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.20,0:04:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  心灵挚友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.13,0:04:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去他永远都找不到女友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.64,0:04:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  你们觉得怎么样…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.28,0:04:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逢  纱江
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.55,0:04:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这么问…我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.87,0:04:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都因为我家哥哥  早上睡得像死猪一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.77,0:04:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从楼梯摔下来长了个瘤子…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.96,0:04:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一早就跟梅原谈起宝贝书的话题…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.63,0:04:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宝贝书？  梅原？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.01,0:04:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  就是说男生们喜欢的那些咸湿书啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.98,0:04:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咸湿书什么的  我觉得每个男生都喜欢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.38,0:04:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.36,0:04:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  你们觉得我家哥哥怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.67,0:04:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得怎么样…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.75,0:04:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚开始虽然觉得他是个怪人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.96,0:04:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.48,0:04:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过深入了解后  我还是个挺有趣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.35,0:04:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.99,0:04:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱江你觉得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.87,0:05:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得他…  是个… 温柔  可靠的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.38,0:05:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.41,0:05:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还是我家的哥哥吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.82,0:05:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.12,0:05:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美也 你喜欢哥哥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.63,0:05:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这么问？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.85,0:05:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为如果不喜欢的话  不会这么在意他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.20,0:05:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦  美也只是担心他的未来而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.06,0:05:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去的话  我觉得他会成为人生输家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.52,0:05:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定连个女友也找不到就大学毕业  然后就业
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.44,0:05:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着还是一如既往讨论着那咸湿书的话题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.90,0:05:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡得像死猪一样  被公司炒鱿鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.25,0:05:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直躲在那做成天文馆似的壁橱里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.28,0:05:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得不会那样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.68,0:05:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘学长没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当真？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.82,0:05:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.07,0:06:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逢跟纱江对老哥的印象  跟美也的不同
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.11,0:06:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道在学校里的老哥  跟在家里的不同吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.22,0:06:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去确定看看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.65,0:06:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  加油  喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.91,0:06:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘同学  谢谢你帮我搬运资料
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.24,0:06:19.11,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.87,0:06:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为绚辻同学兼职着创设祭实行委员跟班长啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.82,0:06:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后有需要帮忙的话随时开口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.98,0:06:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这帮了可大忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.73,0:06:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟绚辻学姐关系好…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.09,0:06:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯一…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.73,0:06:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟  梨穗子  怎么啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.08,0:06:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  作为社团活动的茶点心  我做了烤白薯馅儿的馅儿饼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.05,0:06:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你试吃一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.37,0:06:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又拿我当试验啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.28,0:06:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么说啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.43,0:06:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃的啦  吃吃看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.56,0:06:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.13,0:06:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.78,0:06:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  蛮行嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.20,0:06:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟梨穗子是小时玩伴…  关系好也是理所当然…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.82,0:06:57.94,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}很合我口味呢  是吗  那太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.98,0:07:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼疼疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.04,0:07:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样  服了没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.06,0:07:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要投降的话快说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.79,0:07:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.15,0:07:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.29,0:07:14.68,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}（这是WWE里Chris Jericho的投技 Walls of Jericho）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.29,0:07:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投降吗  投降吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.03,0:07:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投降…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.52,0:07:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胜者  棚町
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.05,0:07:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟棚町学姐的关系也好吧… 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.05,0:07:23.05,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.64,0:07:25.30,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}炒面面包拿来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.71,0:07:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘君  怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.41,0:07:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  森岛学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.50,0:07:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微来治愈下战后的创伤…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.29,0:07:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对了  听我说  听我说 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.72,0:07:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚我看来部很令我感动的电影
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.01,0:07:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电影？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.11,0:07:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.93,0:07:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讲述一个病逝了母亲的小女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.82,0:07:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收养了一只很可爱的小狗的故事喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.10,0:07:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着在床上女孩跟小狗一起睡的场景
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.93,0:07:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起了以前养的JOHN
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.83,0:08:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  橘君  你今天就代替JOHN跟我睡上一觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.24,0:08:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  疼疼疼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.67,0:08:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.17,0:08:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.25,0:08:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然连那森岛学姐都能融洽地在聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.36,0:08:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥羞成那样  真不成体统
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.86,0:08:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 学长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.36,0:08:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海狸的汉羽  够纯爷们的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.75,0:08:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧  不错的角色吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.88,0:08:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写作汉字的汉 有着男人般引人入胜的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.91,0:08:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.01,0:08:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别让美也太担心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.40,0:08:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长要变得再稳重点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.57,0:08:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  这是什么意思  七咲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.14,0:08:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逢跟老哥什么时候开始成了互相交换漫画看的关系了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.62,0:08:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中多同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.78,0:08:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.87,0:08:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工的状况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.50,0:09:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  没问题  还在持续  这都得多亏学长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.37,0:09:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  是你自己的努力啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.83,0:09:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…  学长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.82,0:09:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.78,0:09:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美也怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.01,0:09:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…  那个…  呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.97,0:09:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟纱江也聊得那么开心…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.53,0:09:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此  老哥居然有这么多关系融洽的女生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.85,0:09:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太天真了  美也
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.10,0:09:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你是美也的小时玩伴  跟梨穗子同在二年B班的上崎里沙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.38,0:09:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘  谢谢你对我的说明
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.16,0:09:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过会被发现啦  请保持安静
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.70,0:09:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里沙  你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.54,0:09:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.12,0:09:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  跑掉了  得跟上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.96,0:10:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到跟老哥关系融洽的女生居然有这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.70,0:10:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  所以放不下心来…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.00,0:10:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.87,0:10:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.07,0:10:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  里沙  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.50,0:10:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏你  我才完美地观察到老哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.19,0:10:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别客气  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.73,0:10:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我把你当成我的妹妹啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.62,0:10:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里沙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.02,0:10:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以随时随地叫我家姊喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.65,0:10:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是亲生姐姐  家姊我叫不出口啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.18,0:10:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.85,0:10:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道老哥他意外地受欢迎…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.76,0:11:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为啥找不到女友呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.34,0:11:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.46,0:11:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美也在干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.89,0:11:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别吓我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.77,0:11:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.35,0:11:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咋了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.74,0:11:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对了  你对七咲跟中多说啥了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.16,0:11:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们都说了奇怪的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.23,0:11:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃… 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.06,0:11:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会努力…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.16,0:11:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.91,0:11:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算老哥是个基佬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.95,0:11:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会努力了解你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.12,0:11:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以别一个人苦恼  一切都跟我商量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.52,0:11:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  刚才你说啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.67,0:11:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别一个人苦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.62,0:11:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  再前一句
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.28,0:11:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会努力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.59,0:11:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更后面那句  啊  是前面…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.65,0:11:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算老哥是个基佬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.13,0:11:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  这里  就这里 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.63,0:11:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么变成这样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.00,0:12:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为老哥明明有那么多女生朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.73,0:12:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却还是个寡佬…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.60,0:12:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…  我想难不成你会是个基佬…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.53,0:12:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上也跟梅原握手…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.43,0:12:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是误会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.73,0:12:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美也你也会跟朋友握手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.57,0:12:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.67,0:12:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不可能是基佬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.07,0:12:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当真？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.92,0:12:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当真
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.92,0:12:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.87,0:12:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.79,0:12:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢女孩子  何况还非常喜欢活塞运动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.13,0:12:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  我到底在对妹妹说啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.87,0:12:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.61,0:12:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  美也  这样不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.09,0:12:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我喜欢女孩子  也非常喜欢活塞运动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.36,0:12:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不是啦…  美也听我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.21,0:12:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美也
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.22,0:13:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是…  知道老哥不是基佬我就安心了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.19,0:13:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在怀疑这种事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.33,0:13:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过里沙没想过吗 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.86,0:13:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能跟那么多女生关系融洽  但却找不到女友…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.33,0:13:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成他是个基佬…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.01,0:13:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.49,0:13:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的收藏还一如既往地在不段增加
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.73,0:13:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.77,0:13:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过太好了  这样下去他也会找到女友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.02,0:13:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能还会在圣诞节…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.22,0:13:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.24,0:13:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如突然交到的伴侣会很快就散伙这不是老生常谈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.64,0:13:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以果然还是要找个经常在关注他的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.25,0:13:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道他的性趣的话  任何要求都能够满足
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.91,0:13:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不太明白  不过也差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.66,0:13:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  所以随时都可以叫我家姊喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.98,0:14:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里沙是我的朋友啦   家姊我叫不出口…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.56,0:14:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.03,0:14:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  橘同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.99,0:14:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.20,0:14:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  虽然没谈过话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.62,0:14:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隔壁班的男生…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.01,0:14:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从很久前我就开始关注你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.10,0:14:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在观察…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.65,0:14:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为橘同学有很多粉丝  我是准备放弃了的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.67,0:14:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  今天偶然相遇…  我觉得这是机会…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.55,0:14:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你  请跟我交往
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.34,0:14:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么拒绝他了呢  蛮帅气的男生嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.21,0:14:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是你喜欢的类型？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.03,0:14:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苦恼的话  一切都可以跟家姊商量喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.35,0:15:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  里沙  我先回去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.24,0:15:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟别人交往什么的…  喜欢  讨厌…什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.37,0:15:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有点搞不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.79,0:15:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…  老哥的心情也跟我一样？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.10,0:15:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来  回来得够晚的  干嘛去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.88,0:15:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…  去买了点东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.96,0:15:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  爸妈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.14,0:15:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一如既往的晚归啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.87,0:15:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  喵？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.14,0:15:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美  美也  回房间换衣服咯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.63,0:15:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.16,0:15:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去那边不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.92,0:16:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  在吵什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.09,0:16:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.95,0:16:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小喵咪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.31,0:16:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只要长眼睛的都会知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.66,0:16:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪捡到的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.46,0:16:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还回去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.83,0:16:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.01,0:16:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它在公园孤伶伶的喔  很可怜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.91,0:16:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽是可怜  你也知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.94,0:16:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸妈都对猫敏感啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.12,0:16:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟它失散了的母猫可能也在寻找它喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.49,0:16:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会跟你一起去找啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.59,0:16:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪捡的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.85,0:16:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那附近
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.42,0:16:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  总之过去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.35,0:16:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.47,0:16:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪美也一意孤行地把它带回家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.58,0:17:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今母猫可能在很担心它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.48,0:17:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能在拼命地在找
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.32,0:17:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美也
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.14,0:17:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点让它回到妈妈那吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.85,0:17:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.30,0:17:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.84,0:17:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.17,0:17:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见不到母猫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.97,0:17:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.47,0:17:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微分头找找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.56,0:17:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  加油找喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.44,0:17:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥找到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.85,0:17:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没  没看到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.36,0:18:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能到别的地方了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.48,0:18:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.45,0:18:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.29,0:18:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么冷的话  下起雪的话  它会死掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.54,0:18:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母猫也会…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.90,0:18:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.04,0:18:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母猫估计没事  毕竟长大了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.81,0:18:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那它呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.42,0:18:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法啦  今晚只好带它回去咯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.19,0:18:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过那样的话…  
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.14,0:18:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天再来找母猫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.44,0:18:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.76,0:18:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会说服爸妈的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.33,0:18:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.25,0:18:42.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.77,0:18:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢老哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.58,0:18:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有今晚喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.28,0:18:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有照料小喵咪的工作都得你负责
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.46,0:18:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.50,0:18:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 小喵咪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.15,0:18:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那么去买点猫粮就回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.74,0:18:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.70,0:19:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小喵咪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.38,0:19:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只猫是它的妈妈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.72,0:19:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.60,0:19:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.34,0:19:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你妈妈没错  错的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.32,0:19:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把你带回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.31,0:19:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不准咬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.77,0:19:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美也  那不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.83,0:19:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.12,0:19:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是甜咬啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.20,0:19:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜咬？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.80,0:19:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵咪啊  经常会对母猫和兄弟猫进行甜咬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.90,0:19:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是在淘气啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.00,0:19:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.57,0:19:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  所以母猫也不是在反感吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.18,0:19:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.64,0:19:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在甜咬着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.53,0:19:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真妈妈重逢很开心  所以在甜咬喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.59,0:19:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是爱的表现啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.14,0:20:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.18,0:20:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家人真好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.76,0:20:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.13,0:20:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如老哥所说的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.20,0:20:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.26,0:20:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母猫在拼命地找
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.11,0:20:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这么冷的天气里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.65,0:20:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.18,0:20:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然家人团聚是最好不过的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.48,0:20:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.77,0:20:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.38,0:20:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 老哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.52,0:20:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.21,0:20:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.64,0:20:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.16,0:20:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.40,0:20:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.48,0:20:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美也要是迷路了  你也会找我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.14,0:20:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像小喵咪一样迷路了的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.42,0:20:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会找我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.99,0:20:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别问这么没智商的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.93,0:20:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然会去找你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.88,0:20:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我珍贵的妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.86,0:20:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.63,0:21:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定会找到你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.54,0:21:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.90,0:21:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美也？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.68,0:21:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥你面向前面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.68,0:21:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别问啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.27,0:21:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.98,0:21:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.84,0:21:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.46,0:21:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  喂  干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.06,0:21:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.86,0:21:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶你个头
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.95,0:21:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为啥突然咬过来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.26,0:21:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也对老哥进行甜咬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.15,0:21:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是爱的表现
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.36,0:21:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  喂  疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.99,0:21:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不许逃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.05,0:21:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饶了我吧  美也
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.68,0:21:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我洗  我洗  我洗  我洗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.70,0:21:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然会去找你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.58,0:21:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我珍贵的妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.16,0:22:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥虽然有点放荡还有点逊  而且还带点咸湿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.37,0:22:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  他是个好老哥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.05,0:22:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽是无意中觉得的…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.05,0:22:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我似乎明白了老哥为啥能跟各种各样的女生关系融洽的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.04,0:22:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话  大概不久就能找到女友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.78,0:22:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那之前我会代为作其玩伴  喔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.12,0:22:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.68,0:22:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥  你个咸湿佬  蠢老哥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.71,0:22:43.13,uta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\an2}いつも陽だまりのように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.15,0:22:50.11,uta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\an2}暖かく包んでくれる  大好きな場所
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.15,0:22:52.36,uta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\an2}いつでも側に居れば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.38,0:22:59.00,uta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\an2}優しい気持ちになれるの  ホッとする
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.86,0:23:15.45,uta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\an2}流れる雲はどこへ向かうの?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.36,0:23:23.27,uta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\an2}問い掛けても頼りない返事ばかり
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.37,0:23:27.04,uta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\an2}「ねぇ、ちゃんと聞いてる?」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.68,0:23:32.34,uta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\an2}猫に聞いても困った顔してる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.44,0:23:37.27,uta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\an2}花に聞いても分からない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.33,0:23:39.35,uta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\an2}陽だまりは今日もそっと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.36,0:23:46.40,uta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\an2}暖かく包んでくれる  大切な場所
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.43,0:23:48.90,uta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\an2}見上げる空はいつも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.95,0:23:55.49,uta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\an2}変わらない笑顔溢れる  優しく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.66,0:24:00.00,uta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\an2}もう少し  今はこのままで
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.09,0:24:07.00,uta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\an2}見守ってあげよう  側で
